Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late, I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.99,0:00:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go, I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:05.78,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"The Search"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Man, what a close call.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came this close to being late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pretty unusual, Chitoge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was just barely,\Nfor you to get here before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chitoge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You lost your ribbon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice till I got to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you were in a hurry,\Nthe knot might have been too loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not even sure\Nwhere you might have dropped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go look for it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up, hold up! Class is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, calm down, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you look for it\Nafter school, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that ribbon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your cherished ribbon that\Nyou got from Ms. Hana, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you that I'll find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's one thing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.25,0:03:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one that y—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never fear, Young Mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, shall help with the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pitch in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let me tie this up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.85,0:03:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would\Ncome in handy one day, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My hair/makeup kit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, what kind of\Nstyle should we go for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Over a ribbon...\Nhow pathetic you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine that anyone would\Nturn in that strip of cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By now it might well be discarded\Nalong with the trash, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marika Tachibana! Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really think that's\Nwhat happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not at all how you'd usually react!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.14,0:03:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I implore you not to sob so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:04:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, shall lend\Na hand in the search,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so for goodness sake,\Nplease stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she okay? Chitoge...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where it could be?\NChitoge's ribbon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like anything resembling it\Nwas turned in at the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Young Mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, cheer up, Chitoge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help you look again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what am I gonna do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, today, as a special treat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy you some ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That limited-edition ramen that you love\Ncame back on the menu lately, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When we find your ribbon,\Nlet's all go out for...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks. I'm not in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did she just turn down ramen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I-I mean it's ramen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's never done that before, not once!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, look how meek she's gotten.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not a matter of being thrown off...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just can't stand to see her like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, but what is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I'm imagining\Nthings, but somehow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is she like, a stunner now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Normally, it's hard to forget, but\Nshe's always been a stunner, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Somehow, together with that meekness,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.42,0:05:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she looks more feminine\Nthan usual to me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna arm-wrestle with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind why.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ready... set...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was a fool for getting my faint hopes up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, but if we never do find that\Nribbon, what's gonna happen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be that she'll\Nstay this way forever?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We just can't seem to find\Nyour ribbon, Young Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where else can we look for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We might have to\Nexpand our search area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at her, mired in depression again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really can't take this anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I could somehow cheer her up,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but that ribbon's nowhere to be found.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like Tachibana said, even if\Nsomeone did pick up that ribbon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's doubtful that they'd turn it in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no choice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's killing me to trick her like this, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.38,0:07:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found it! I found your ribbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Did you really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, it got blown away\Ninto some alley, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.39,0:07:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Try not to lose it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.43,0:07:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! Thank you so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It smells different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It smells like it's brand-new.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My bad! I'm sorry I tried to trick you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.33,0:07:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But see... I didn't\Nmean you any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No... that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did that for me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:07:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's up with that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The normal you would totally kick\Nmy butt, bury me in the ground,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and stomp off, shouting\Nall kinds of abuse!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who the hell are you, anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But no matter how you look at it,\Nthat one's the awful Chitoge, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.65,0:08:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It just might be better\Nfor her to stay this way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no! No way would that be better!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came this close to being\Ndeceived by a gentle lie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No choice, then. I'll just\Nstart all over and look for it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chitoge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got great eyesight, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That thing caught\Nin the telephone pole...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found it, found it, found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:09:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I should be glad\Nthat you've cheered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've lost sight of it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm gonna find it, no matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Found it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna catch it this time for sure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hold up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}N-No way...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this crying for, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Raku...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because... my ribbon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's the ribbon that I bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My ribbon just got\Nblown away by the wind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.12,0:10:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were chasing after the wrong one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And just now, I picked up your ribbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell by the smell, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go on and make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.94,0:11:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... Next time, be sure to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you glomming\Nonto me, moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never lose you again, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, man...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So she's finally back to\Nbeing her usual self, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems just a little too bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... this feels more natural, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why are you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:58.79,Title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Just Testing"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:10.30,DefaultBot2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A LITTLE LOVE HERE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Confess...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no, no... Not\Nhappening, not happening!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.87,0:12:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If... If I did...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what would happen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.75,0:12:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for how I feel about him... Well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I like him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But as for whether or not\NI want to date him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be honest, I'm not sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it that I want to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.11,0:13:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do I want this to end up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I did confess my feelings,\Nwould it change anything?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I do it? As a test.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as a test?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not for real.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just see what it's like to say it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NStaring at me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible! Absolutely impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.85,0:13:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just the thought of confessing my\Nfeelings to him makes my head explode!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because if he turns me down,\Nwhat am I gonna do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We still have to keep up\Nthis fake love afterwards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way could I take that!\NI'd totally die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I really did tell him how I feel,\Nwhat kind of look would he give me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would he be happy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Would he be disgusted?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet he'd be disgusted!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, he doesn't even\Nsee me as the girlfriend type.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you pondering this\Nso seriously, Chitoge?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just testing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're only testing out this thought!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.31,DefaultBot2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:20.31,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't Say It...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can't tell him directly,\Nwhy don't I write him a love letter?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That seems like it would be much easier.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, what am I supposed to write?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I love you, please\Ngo out with me!" I guess?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:50.92,DefaultTopLeft,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No Way
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:50.92,DefaultMid,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't Write That
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:50.92,DefaultBot2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's no good! I can't write that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I know I'm not\Nreally handing it to him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's so embarrassing, I can't take it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My heart's pounding harder\Nthan I'd ever imagined.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.97,0:15:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did all the couples in the world get through\Nthese rituals to become couples?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aren't they all beyond heroic?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. No letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.89,0:15:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let me practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You see... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I..."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you! Please go out with me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I managed to say it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although it was horribly embarrassing,\NI managed to say it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess if I'm\Ntalking to a doll, it's no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Young Mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was just me practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I was just\Nmimicking some TV show!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Tsugumi, would you\Nmind knocking? Knocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did knock, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Confessing your\Nfeelings is hard, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was just practice, and look at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it were for real...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.38,DefaultBot,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totally Impossible (>_<)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.38,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder how everybody else does it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who confessed their\Nfeelings first, you or Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, long story short, it was me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I never\Ntold you how I met Hana, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.02,0:16:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana and I met when I happened to\Nbe here in Japan on business, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It happened one day when we were trading\Ngunshots with an enemy organization
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in an abandoned factory...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like the pressure's on us, eh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What do you want to do, Boss?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}W-What's up with that woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who the hell is she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she out of her mind?\NWalking right into a hail of bullets...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This woman stood right in the crossfire,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.77,0:17:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and this is what she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which of you people called in\Nthe order for this pizza?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean that was Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, Hana was\Na struggling student, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was juggling seventeen\Npart-time jobs just to get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seventeen? What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, Hana was so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looking just like an angel\Nwho'd descended onto a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In spite of myself, I was\Ncaptivated by the sight of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you do after that, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right... I proposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you marry me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately afterwards, I got\Nthe living daylights kicked out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mom's something else, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it was\Nlove at first sight for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I had my work\Ncut out for afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I kept making moves on her,\Nbut she'd always shoot me down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and in the worst cases I'd end up with\Nbroken bones during the rejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No good, this is too\Natypical to be of any help.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the thing is, despite all that,\NI couldn't stand not to tell her how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how alluring she was to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure she was the one\NI was destined to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.72,0:18:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Dad was really in love with Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I can\Npull that off just like he did?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't seem like I can even pretend\Nto confess my feelings for him, so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I really tell him that I love him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chitoge! Ahead of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:50.26,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wound
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you shut up! Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spacing out and crashing into a sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How scatterbrained is that, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.34,0:19:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lately you've been brooding over\Nsomething, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something I can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind being\Nyour sounding board.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's been worried about me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That kind of makes me happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, we might have\Nthe tiniest bit of chemistry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no... is that\Na reason to confess?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if you're in love with him,\Nthat's what you should do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you do it, something might change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you really love him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This might be your chance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you came to Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we started\Npretending to be dating...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been\Nmore than a year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, huh? I'm used to it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I'm used to such\Nan abnormal situation scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that? Are you\Ncomplaining about the status quo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It just blows my mind, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So much happened, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Getting clobbered by you,\Nclobbered by you, clobbered by you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! It was all\Nyour fault, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was mostly beyond\Nmy control, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you were so pissed\Nabout this whole thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But of course I'd resign myself!\NSince I'm an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's this adult you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see the lady before your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, not seeing her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna clobber you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, but you don't\Nmind me now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but we still have more than halfway\Nto go before we graduate, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no use thinking about\Nwhat's gonna happen in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just take our time with this.\NWe'll figure it out somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take our time, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:20:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I have to\Ndo it right this minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's private!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to spend more time with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, that's\Nhow I feel towards him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we head back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If my feelings of love\Nfor this guy don't change,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.11,0:21:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then someday I'll want to\Nconfess to him like my dad did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that day ever comes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.53,0:21:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it wasn't nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:21:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I treat you to some ramen today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me, treat lowly you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you?\NYou got a fever or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why would your\Nmind go there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because normally, that would\Nnever happen in a million...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.73,0:22:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you... shut up!
